Package it.polimi.deib.se2019.sanp4.adrenaline.controller.match

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    ScoreManager
    An abstract class representing an object that is responsible of assigning points to users according to the current state of the game
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    MatchController
    It is responsible for controlling the flow of the game, from the beginning to the end
    SpawnController
    Provides static methods to handle initial spawn and respawn after death.
    StandardScoreManager
    A specialized class describing an object that is responsible of assigning points to users It represents the standard scoring mechanism of the game, as described in the game manual
    TurnController
    It is responsible for controlling the flow of a single turn.
